#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today‚Äôs topic is about managing stress.\n"
"\n"
"We know how stressful it is to bring up teenagers in these times. Learning to manage your stress helps you ‚Äì and your family."
msgstr ""
"Mada ya leo ni juu ya kudhibiti mafadhaiko.\n"
"\n"
"Tunajua jinsi inavyofadhaisha kulea vijana katika nyakati hizi. Kujifunza kudhibiti msongo wako kunakusaidia wewe na familia yako."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can managing stress help you and your family? Tap play to find out"
msgstr "Je, kudhibiti mfadhaiko kunaweza kukusaidia wewe na familia yako? Gusa cheza ili kujua"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Today's topic is managing stress.\n"
"\n"
"It is important to know how to manage our stress. At times our children can behave in ways that make us feel stressed and us as parents can make our children feel stressed too.\n"
"\n"
"So, it is important to notice when we feel stressed and take a pause and breathe. That will help you manage your stress."
msgstr ""
"Salamu kila mtu.\n"
"\n"
"Mada ya leo ni kudhibiti mafadhaiko.\n"
"\n"
"Ni muhimu kujua jinsi ya kudhibiti mafadhaiko yetu. Wakati fulani watoto wetu wanaweza kuishi kwa njia zinazotufanya tuhisi mfadhaiko na sisi kama wazazi tunaweza kuwafanya watoto wetu wahisi mfadhaiko pia.\n"
"\n"
"Kwa hivyo, ni muhimu kutambua tunapohisi mfadhaiko na kuchukua pumziko na kupumua. Hiyo itakusaidia kudhibiti mafadhaiko yako."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"A few simple habits (like pausing, breathing, and talking calmly) can make your day feel lighter.\n"
"\n"
"When you are calm, your family also feels calmer."
msgstr ""
"Tabia chache rahisi (kama kusimama, kupumua, na kuzungumza kwa utulivu) yanaweza kufanya siku yako kuwa nyepesi.\n"
"\n"
"Pale unapo tulia, Familia yako pia hujisikia utulivu."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_4.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Pause, take a breath. Now hear how taking a simple pause helped @data.characters.media_female_4.name and her teens"
msgstr "Chukua pumziko, pumua. vuta pumzi. Sasa sikia jinsi kuchukua pumziko rahisi kulivyosaidia @data.characters.media_female_4.name na vijana wake"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Life is tough sometimes. Before I joined @global.app_name, I used to be grumpy at all times. I would take out my anger on everyone at home, not only my teens but even my husband as well. They would run away when I came home because they knew I would start yelling at them.\n"
"\n"
"Learning to take a pause and breathe was difficult at first. But every time I tried it, it helped me to calm down. Now my teens are no longer running away when I come home and they actually listen better than when I used to shout at them!"
msgstr ""
"Maisha ni magumu wakati mwingine. Kabla sijajiunga na @global.app_name, nilikuwa nikiudhika kila wakati. Ningetoa hasira zangu kwa kila mtu nyumbani, si tu vijana wangu bali hata mume wangu pia. Hukimbia niliporudi nyumbani kwa sababu walijua ningeanza kuwafokea.\n"
"\n"
"Kujifunza kuchukua pumziko na kupumua ilikuwa ngumu mwanzoni. Lakini kila nilipojaribu, ilinisaidia kutulia. Sasa vijana wangu hawatoroki tena ninaporudi nyumbani na wanasikiliza vizuri zaidi kuliko nilipokuwa nikiwapigia kelele!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let‚Äôs look at an example of how stress can sometimes just get too much, for all of us:"
msgstr "Hebu tuangalie mfano wa jinsi ambavyo wakati mwingine msongo wa mawazo unaweza kutuzidia sana, sisi sote:"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name lost his job. He was sitting at home feeling frustrated and stressed when @data.characters.f1_son_18.name entered the room."
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_father.name alipoteza kazi. Alikuwa amekaa nyumbani akiwa amechanganyikiwa na kufadhaika wakati @data.characters.f1_son_18.name alipoingia chumbani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can I have money to buy some airtime?"
msgstr "Je, ninaweza kupata pesa za kununua muda wa maongezi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Leave me alone and mind your own business!"
msgstr "Niache na uendelee na mambo yako mwenyewe!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What did I do? You never listen!"
msgstr "Nimefanya nini? Huwa husikii!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I said leave me alone or you will get a beating!"
msgstr "Nimesema uniache la sivyo utapata kipigo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look! I have made a house!"
msgstr "Tazama! Nimejenga nyumba!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Who cares about your stupid house!"
msgstr "Nani anajali nyumba yako ya kijinga!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let's think about what happened in this story."
msgstr "Hebu tufikirie kuhusu kilichotokea kwenye hadithi hii."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name's
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you think @data.characters.f1_father.name's son, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, felt?"
msgstr "Je, unafikiri mtoto wa @data.characters.f1_father.name, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, alijisikiaje?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, he did not understand why his father, @data.characters.f1_father.name, got angry, and probably felt all these emotions."
msgstr "Ndiyo, hakuelewa kwa nini baba yake, @data.characters.f1_father.name, alikasirika, na pengine alihisi hisia hizi zote."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name? should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And @data.characters.f1_father.name?"
msgstr "Na @data.characters.f1_father.name?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sad"
msgstr "Huzuni"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Scared"
msgstr "Unaogopa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Confused"
msgstr "Kuchanganyikiwa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Angry"
msgstr "Hasira"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes. He felt stressed and overwhelmed by the situation."
msgstr "Ndiyo. Aliona kuwa na msongo wa mawazo na kuzidiwa na hali."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What could @data.characters.f1_father.name have done differently?"
msgstr "Je, @data.characters.f1_father.name anaweza kufanya nini cha tofauti?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Recognise why he felt stressed"
msgstr "Tambua kwa nini alihisi mfadhaiko"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, when we recognise we feel stressed, we can take a deep breath and respond with calm and understanding. That way we can find solutions together that work."
msgstr "Ndiyo, tunapotambua kwamba tunafadhaiko, tunaweza kuvuta pumzi na kujibu kwa utulivu na kuelewa. Kwa njia hiyo tunaweza kupata masuluhisho pamoja yanayofanya kazi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Take a deep breath and speak calmly"
msgstr "Kuvuta pumzi ndefu na kuzungumza kwa utulivu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Show he understands his teen's feelings"
msgstr "Onyesha kwamba anaelewa hisia za kijana wake"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Think about solutions together with @data.characters.f1_son_18.name"
msgstr "Fikiria kuhusu suluhu pamoja na @data.characters.f1_son_18.name"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Do something positive together with @data.characters.f1_son_18.name"
msgstr "Fanya kitu chanya pamoja na @data.characters.f1_son_18.name"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, when we recognise we feel stressed, we can take a deep breath and respond with calm and understanding. That way we can find solutions together that make everyone feel better."
msgstr "Ndiyo, tunapotambua kwamba tunafadhaika, tunaweza kuvuta pumzi na kujibu kwa utulivu na kuelewa. Kwa njia hiyo tunaweza kupata suluhu pamoja ambazo zinafanya kila mtu ajisikie vizuri."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let‚Äôs go back in time and see what might happen if @data.characters.f1_father.name tries something different."
msgstr "Hebu turudi nyuma kwa wakati and tuone kile kinachoweza kutokea kama @data.characters.f1_father.name atajaribu kitu tofauti."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name realised that his behaviour affected everyone‚Äôs mood and responses. Let‚Äôs see what he does to make things better."
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_father.name alitambua kwamba tabia yake ilikuwa na athari kwa hisia na majibu ya kila mtu. Hebu tuone nini alichofanya mambo kuwa bora zaidi."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name,
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"@data.characters.f1_son_18.name, @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name, I am sorry for getting angry. Since losing my job, I feel very stressed and tired from looking for work every day. \n"
"\n"
"I know this is also hard for you. How are you feeling?"
msgstr ""
"@data.characters.f1_son_18.name, @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name, Nisamehe kwa hasira zangu. Tangu kupoteza kazi yangu, Najihisi kuwa na msongo mkubwa wa mawazo na kuchoka kutokana na kutafuta kazi kila siku.\n"
"\n"
"Ninajua kwamba hii pia ni ngumu kwako. Wewe unahisije?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I feel worried when I need to ask for anything. The answer is always no..."
msgstr "Nahisi wasiwasi napo hitaji kuuliza chochote. Jibu kila wakati ni hapana..."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I also feel worried. I want to help, but I don‚Äôt know how."
msgstr "Najisikia kuwa na wasiwasi pia. Nilitaka kusaidia, Lakini sijui kwa namna gani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You two are amazing. You've been carrying so much burden. We want to provide everything you need, but things like airtime and private tutoring cost a lot of money."
msgstr "Ninyi wawili ni ajabu. Mlichukua mizingo mizito sana. Tunataka kuwapa kila kitu mnachohitaji, lakini mambo kama muda wa maongezi na kufundishwa binafsi vina gharimu pesa nyingi sana."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I have an idea! @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name is really good at maths. Maybe she can help @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name with homework so we don‚Äôt need a tutor?"
msgstr "Nina wazo! @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name ni mzuri kwenye hisabati. Labda anaweza kukusaidia @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name na kazi za nyumbani kwa hiyo hatuhitaji mwalimu?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes! I like learning with her!"
msgstr "Ndiyo! Ninapenda kujifunza na yeye!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That‚Äôs a wonderful idea. Thank you both for thinking of a solution together. I am really proud of you."
msgstr "Hilo ni wazo zuri sana. Asanteni nyote wawili kwa kufikiria suluhisho pamoja. Ninajivunia sana ninyi."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"We learned a lot from @data.characters.f1_father.name about making things better, even after getting angry.\n"
"\n"
"Now, let‚Äôs think about your own life. What helps you feel calm in a stressful moment?"
msgstr ""
"Tumejifunza mengi sana kutoka @data.characters.f1_father.name kuhusu kuboresha mambo, hata baada ya kukasirika.\n"
"\n"
"Sasa, hebu waza kuhusu maisha yako. Nini kinaweza kusaidia wewe kujisikia utulivu wakati wa msongo wa mawazo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What can help you feel calm in a stressful moment?"
msgstr "Nini kinaweza kusaidia wewe kujisikia utulivu wakati wa msongo wa mawazo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Take 5 breaths"
msgstr "Vuta pumzi 5"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Walk away for a moment"
msgstr "Tembea mbali kwa muda"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Share how you feel"
msgstr "Shirikisha jinsi unavyohisi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Nice! Sharing feelings can reduce stress."
msgstr "Vizuri! Kushirikisha hisia kunaweza kupunguza msongo wa mawazo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Talk to a friend"
msgstr "Ongea na rafiki"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Great idea!\n"
"\n"
"Pausing in your own way doesn‚Äôt make the situation easier, but it helps you feel less overwhelmed and more in control."
msgstr ""
"Wazo zuri!\n"
"\n"
"Kusimama kwa njia yako mwenyewe haifanyi njia kuwa rahisi, lakini inasaidia wewe kujihisi kuzidiwa kidogo na kuwa na udhibiti zaidi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are a few skills to help you manage stress that you can use with your teens!"
msgstr "Hapa kuna ujuzi mdogo wa kukusaidia kudhibiti mfadhaiko ambayo unaweza kutumia na vijana wako!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "BREATHE"
msgstr "VUTA PUMZI"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Breathe slowly. Pause.\n"
"\n"
"Before you say anything, slowly breathe in and out five times. It will calm you, and give you a chance to think."
msgstr ""
"Pumua polepole. Sitisha.\n"
"\n"
"Kabla ya kusema chochote, pumua polepole ndani na nje mara tano. Itakutuliza, na kukupa nafasi ya kufikiria."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SHARE"
msgstr "KUSHIRIKISHANA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Share how you feel.\n"
"\n"
"This is hard. Many of us were told not to cry, or show our feelings to our children. But take a deep breath and calmly tell them how you feel. They will understand better, and also learn from you how to deal with stress."
msgstr ""
"Shirikisha namna unahisi.\n"
"\n"
"Hili ni jambo gumu. Wengi wetu tuliambiwa tusilie, au kuonesha hisia zetu kwa watoto wetu. Lakini vuta pumzi ndefu na uwaambie kwa utulivu jinsi unavyohisi. Wataelewa vizuri, na pia watajifunza kutoka kwako jinsi ya kukabiliana na msongo wa mawazo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SHOW"
msgstr "ONESHA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Show them you care.\n"
"\n"
"This is also hard! Stress makes us focus on ourselves. But our teens need our support. Ask them how they feel. Listen to them and comfort them. Try a hug or say \"I understand\". It can change everything."
msgstr ""
"Waonyeshe unajali.\n"
"\n"
"Hili pia ni jambo gumu! Msongo wa mawazo hutufanya tujiangalie sisi wenyewe. Lakini vijana wetu wanahitaji msaada wetu. Waulize wanajisikiaje. Wasikilize na uwafariji. Jaribu kuwakumbatia au sema \"Ninaelewa\". Kufanya hivyo kunaweza kubadilisha kila kitu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SEEK"
msgstr "TAFUTA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Seek the positive.\n"
"\n"
"Can you and your teen think about ideas that might help? Can you do something positive together to take your mind off the stress?"
msgstr ""
"Tafuta kitu chanya.\n"
"\n"
"Je, wewe na kijana wako mnaweza kufikiria mawazo yanayoweza kusaidia? Je, mnaweza kufanya pamoja kitu chanya ili kuhamisha mawazo yako kutoka kwenye msongo wa mawazo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This week's home activity is to respond calmly when you feel stressed.\n"
"\n"
"Whenever you feel stressed or upset with your teen, pause and take five slow breaths before you react. When you are both calm, share how you feel with each other."
msgstr ""
"Hii wiki shughuli za nyumbani ni kujibu kwa utulivu unapojisikia msongo wa mawazo.\n"
"\n"
"Wakati wowote unapohisi msongo wa mawazo na hasira na kijana wako, simama na shusha pumzi polepole mara tano kabla ya kujibu. Wakati nyote kwa pamoja mmetulia, shirikisha jinsi unavyojisikia kwa kila mmoja."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Remember to:** \n"
"\n"
"üòÆ‚Äçüí® BREATHE: take five breaths in and out before you react\n"
"ü§ùüèæ SHARE: when you're both calm, share with your teen how you feel\n"
"üíô SHOW: ask them how they feel to show you care\n"
"üîç SEEK: find something positive in this situation together"
msgstr ""
"**Kumbuka:** \n"
"\n"
"üòÆ‚Äçüí® PUMUA: vuta pumzi tano ndani na nje kabla hujajibu\n"
"ü§ùüèæ SHIRIKI: nyote wawili mkiwa watulivu, shiriki na kijana wako jinsi unavyohisi\n"
"üíô ONYESHA: waulize wanajisikiaje ili kukuonyesha kujali\n"
"üîç TAFUTA: pata kitu chanya katika hali hii pamoja"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you try taking five slow breaths before responding this week?"
msgstr "Unaweza kujaribu kuchukua pumzi tano za taratibu kabla ya kujibu wiki hii?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ndiyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Great! Pausing to breathe before reacting will help your whole family feel calmer."
msgstr "Vizuri! Kusimama kwa kushusha pumzi kabla ya kujibu kutasaidia familia yako yote kuhisi utulivu zaidi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Nafikiri hivyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That‚Äôs a good start. When you are stressed, remember to take a few deep breaths, it will make it easier to respond calmly."
msgstr "Huo ni mwanzo mzuri. Unapofadhaika, kumbuka kuchukua pumzi chache za kina, itafanya iwe rahisi kujibu kwa utulivu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hapana"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I understand, sometimes we just don‚Äôt have capacity. Try to keep spending time with your teen - whenever you are ready you can practise responding calmly and find a Safety Word together."
msgstr "Ninaelewa, wakati mwingine hatuna uwezo. Jaribu kutumia muda na kijana wako - wakati wowote unapokuwa tayari unaweza kujizoeza kujibu kwa utulivu na kutafuta Neno la Usalama pamoja."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember, when we practice responding calmly and sharing how we feel, our teens learn to do the same. This skill will help them their whole life!"
msgstr "Kumbuka, tunapojizoesha kujibu kwa utulivu na kushirikishana jinsi tunavyohisi, vijana wetu hujifunza kufanya vivyo hivyo. Ustadi huu utawasaidia maisha yao yote!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_son_1.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hear how @data.characters.media_son_1.name learned to stay calm from his father"
msgstr "Sikia jinsi @data.characters.media_son_1.name alivyojifunza kuwa mtulivu kutoka kwa baba yake"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Whenever I would do something wrong, my father would get so angry at me and beat me. He would not even listen to me and I would get so angry as well at him and everyone else.\n"
"\n"
"Now, when he gets angry, he first takes a few deep breaths before he responds. It makes everyone calm down instead of causing a big fight.\n"
"\n"
"It really helped me at home and at school, because even me I am no longer slashing everyone and I am no longer this moody person. When I feel really angry or stressed, I also take deep breaths like my father does. I am a different person."
msgstr ""
"Pindi nilipofanya kitu kibaya, Baba yangu alinikasirikia sana na kunipiga. Alikuwa hanisikilizi na hii ilinifanya kumkasirikia yeye pamoja na watu wengine.\n"
"\n"
"Sasa, pindi anapokuwa na hasira, anachukua dakika chache kuvuta pumzi ndefu kabla hajajibu chochote. Inafanya kila mtu kutulia badala ya kusababisha ugomvi mkubwa.\n"
"\n"
"Hii inanisaidia sana nyumbani na hata shuleni, hata Mimi sasa siwakasirikii wengine na si mtu wa hisia kali. Pindi ninapojihisi hasira au mwenye msongo wa mawazo, Navuta pumzi ndefu kama Baba yangu anavyofanya. Nimekuwa mtu tofauti."

